Enum DlmsUnit

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<DlmsUnit>

    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<DlmsUnit>

    public enum DlmsUnit
extends java.lang.Enum<DlmsUnit>
    The units as defined in IEC 62056-62. Some units not defined in IEC 62056-62 but needed by M-Bus were added.
